This week I am sharing my TOP FIVE FAVORITE DIY's of 2020 that Mike and I did together. I am celebrating all the good things we accomplished in 2020 and counting the blessings we had in such a crazy year. 

🎊#5 Laminate Flooring Install 

This was a long project that wasn't hard but was time-consuming. We are so glad we did it! We used NUTMEG from @officialselectsurfaces and absolutely LOVE it. 

I added 7 inch MDF trim on the baseboards to add a modern look. Still working on getting them all painted, one year later!! 🙈
.
Credit: @citygirlmeetsfarmboy
